{"type":"message","id":"aef434b9","parentId":"5ca607b9","timestamp":"2026-02-27T18:17:50.648Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"ngrok 没有安装。我需要指导用户安装 ngrok，然后配置 webhook。让我提供完整的步骤。","thinkingSignature":"reasoning_content"},{"type":"text","text":"好的，需要安装 ngrok 并配置。步骤如下：\n\n## 1. 安装 ngrok\n\n```bash\n# 用 Homebrew 安装\nbrew install ngrok\n\n# 或者去官网下载：https://ngrok.com/download\n```\n\n## 2. 注册 ngrok 账号并获取 Token\n\n去 https://dashboard.ngrok.com/signup 注册，然后在 dashboard 里找到 **Your Authtoken**。\n\n## 3. 配置 ngrok Token\n\n```bash\nngrok config add-authtoken 你的_TOKEN\n```\n\n## 4. 启动 ngrok\n\n```bash\nngrok http 18789\n```\n\n你会看到类似这样的输出：\n```\nForwarding  https://abc123def.ngrok-free.app -> http://localhost:18789\n```\n\n**复制那个 `https://...ngrok-free.app` 的 URL**。\n\n## 5. 更新 OpenClaw 配置\n\n把刚才复制的 URL 告诉我（或者你自己改 `~/.openclaw/config.yaml`）：\n\n```yaml\ntelegram:\n  enabled: true\n  webhook:\n    enabled: true\n    url: \"https://abc123def.ngrok-free.app/webhook/telegram\"  # 你的 ngrok URL\n```\n\n## 6. 重启 Gateway\n\n```bash\nopenclaw gateway restart\n```\n\n---\n\n**现在到哪一步了？需要我等你操作完，还是你已经跑起来了？**"}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"moonshot","model":"kimi-k2.5","usage":{"input":315,"output":319,"cacheRead":48640,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":49274,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"stop","timestamp":1772216261045}}
